//=== DESTROYER QUANTUM V28.06 — TEST: Leviathan Kelly Fraction Boost ===
// VENI VIDI VICI
// Tests: Leviathan_KellyFraction 0.35 → 0.50 (+43%)
// Starting from AGGRESSIVE baseline — ONLY this parameter changed.
// Rationale: HIGH impact — Kelly fraction controls how aggressively
// Leviathan allocates capital to high-confidence setups. At 0.35 it
// already allocates 40% more than Moderate (0.25). Pushing to 0.50
// means Leviathan goes "half-Kelly" — the theoretical optimal for
// maximizing long-term growth in favorable setups.
// Target: Push from $68K toward $75K+
//
//=== CORE RISK ===
InpBase_Risk_Percent=1.5
InpBase_Risk_Percent_H1=0.4
